Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:10.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's scratched, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You made this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:22.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anyone except you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:27.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Honestly, please tell me\Nwhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:31.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where's your school? the name of your parents?\Nyour address, telephone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:40.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyagawa, has my son\Ncaused you some problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:42.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kiryu-kun, he's your son?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:46.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He has, look at this scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:49.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:59.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I expect reimbursement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:03.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:09.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:11.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,could you hold me tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:14.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:19.05,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Finally, my full-fledged medical examination started with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:28.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:31.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Does a psychiatrist have an exchange\Nlike that with a patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are Yumeno-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:35.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hino-rin,\Ncould you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:38.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,deceiving Akira.\N{\3c&H573235&}I'm not deceiving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:40.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, why\Nwere you holding her tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:43.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In this way, I want to talk to you\Nlooking at your face..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:47.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want a guy like this to hug you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,because a guy like him\Nwill only betray your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:53.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's useless to believe in him! Do not believe in him, at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:07.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:09.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What? Are you just going to stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:16.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There are times when you want to strike\Nthings or people in that way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please continue until you're satisfied.\N{\3c&H573235&}Don't say things as you understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:22.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Once you're calm down,\Nlet's drink some tea together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:27.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is that you want to expel\Na patient like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:31.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The other day when we went to the sea,\NAkira-san also did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she hand over some tea for me,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:37.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:46.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please come out, Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:54.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, if you want to stay there it's fine,\Nlet's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:27.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., I\Ndid something that caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:38.56,Self tought,,0,0,0,,When the therapist is facing patients\Nwith dissociative identity disorder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:43.06,Self tought,,0,0,0,,he should never take the attitude\Nof denying neither of the personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do I have this disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:51.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is the reason?\NLet's look together for the cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,of this strange thing that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:59.54,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Because the other personality might be hearing the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It'll work if we can talk about it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:15.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,then, today, please tell me about\Nthe childhood memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was always painting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because I was really shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr.\NI'm sorry, again such a thing..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it,\NShinya-kun, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry\Nfor scattering them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:38.11,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun, the only son of Kiryu Kaoru-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:42.07,Self tought,,0,0,0,,with Savant syndrome, involving disabilities in language,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.07,Self tought,,0,0,0,,called an autism spectrum disorder, it's an special case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:49.58,Self tought,,0,0,0,,having an unique wonderful view of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:54.06,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:58.63,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.05,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.57,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:14.05,Self tought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:19.12,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:29.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:49.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Seppuku Monaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you want to apologize with a disemboweled belly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By all means, I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'd like to take Yumeno-chan\Nouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is she available?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:05.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Soon, I have to genuinely persuade\NIke, the Press secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have to receive permission\Nfor a new hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:13.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking of\Nletting her rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because she was missing at the "Higashi Odori"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,negotiate with the Shinbashi association.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No,\Nit's not just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You can not just refuse to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:38.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there are any reasons just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sick? Is she hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:50.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, she's sleeping at the Okiya?\NWho's the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Our Hino Rintaro?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As usual, it's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But compared to the early days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:16.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but I've the conviction that\NI've come to understand him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:19.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, I still\Ncan't tell what Shinya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:22.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is thinking.\N{\3c&H573235&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:26.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't know it now,\Nhe will surely show you a sign or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just a little while ago, with Dr. Miyagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:34.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya scratched his car with a bicycle\Nthat fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Prof. Miyagawa's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shinya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've always\Nwanted to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, this, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:51.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is his sign,\Nto say 'I'm sorry'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:57.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One step further into connecting\Nwith Shinya-kun's mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As expected of the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd like to think so..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:05.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He does this when he's happy, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:11.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Hino-kun,\Nexplain it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:16.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We're in a middle of examination\NDirector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:19.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, he is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director, excuse me.\NAh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where is Yumeno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:28.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She already left. Can't this wait,\Nsince I'm in a middle of an examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:31.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Yumeno?\N{\3c&H573235&}I can not answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the Director, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Doctors have a duty of confidentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Director himself is telling me\Nto break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:41.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what that attitude means,\Nin this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Someone like you can be fired at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Alright, finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:49.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Pink elephants are rare, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you like elephants?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:26.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's fun to see an elephant jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, {\i1}sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That over there, it's the mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew that you'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:05.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya. Shinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:08.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You like it here, Shinya. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, this is your secret place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It feels good, here outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:19.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Dr. Rintaro,\NWe took a look at your paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:24.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't be more impressed by\Nthe throughout research and study.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:30.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the author, Yoko Kawakami has an interest\Nin the research done at our school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:34.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}please introduce her to me.\NWe would like to welcome her in our lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:37.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}University of Houston school of medicine, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:40.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dean Margaret Goldman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was a very well-made paper,\Nand as we talked before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:48.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was allowed to send it to my old school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:52.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes\N{\3c&H573235&}How do you wish to reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I'm in charge of some patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:58.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please let me think about it a little.\N{\3c&H573235&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Is it okay now?\N{\3c&H573235&}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:09.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know.. something big has happened\N{\3c&H573235&}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:12.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Shinya..\N{\3c&H573235&}What happened to Shinya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He did it\N{\3c&H573235&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:19.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Grand Prix Art Sculpture Exhibition for Children,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:22.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He won it!\N{\3c&H573235&}Isn't that great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:24.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!\N{\3c&H573235&}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr., sorry for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:34.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate together!\NBig time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about this for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That child is probably a case of Savant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:49.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Furthermore,\Nhe may also experience Synesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:54.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Write a paper about your interpretation of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The secrets of this mysterious brain function
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is your area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:03.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:07.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It can be useful,\NLet's do it, Machiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What? What do you want to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You may not be pleased by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:36.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's really irritating that it concerns\Nsuch a virtuous gentleman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:41.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:44.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yumeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:47.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, then, now,\NI'll leave first, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:56.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For leaving the other day and also about the Azuma Odori.\NMy condition was poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And you didn't tell me that you are\Nreceiving treatment from Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who said such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the usual healthy me, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:18.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh..it was well photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who took it?\N{\3c&H573235&}Should i know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:24.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since when you have this with Hino..?\N{\3c&H573235&}Hey.. En-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:27.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's useless to get mad at such a thing,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:32.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, I'm glad you're jealous of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:45.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-chan..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi,\Nthank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:56.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, next is\NProf. Miyagawa, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today, I'd like to ask everyone\Nfor your cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,regarding my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For some time now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:13.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've been studying the\Nconnection between mental disorders and the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Among them,\NI'm proud of calling myself an expert
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,regarding Autism and brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:24.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This time, the patient I'd like to study this time is this person,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:28.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he's also Dr. Hino's patient,\NKiryuu Shinya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh? Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:34.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun while being a case of autism spectrum disorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:37.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he also has a rare talent for sculpting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:41.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Recently, he has been awarded with the\NGrand Prix Art Sculpture Exhibition for Children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I dare say, he was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,diagnosed as one of the cases\Nreferred as Savant syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so, Dr. Hino?\N{\3c&H573235&}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:54.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,People with Savant syndrome\Nhave an ability to recall images,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,sounds, or objects in memory\Nafter only a few instances of exposure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:00.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After hearing only once\Nthey can reproduce a tune
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,they have an exceptional memory.\N{\3c&H573235&}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:07.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, different letters will induce\Nthe experience of particular colors
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:10.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the sounds will induce the experience\Nof a particular shape and smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:13.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I believe it combines synesthesia,\Nin which the stimulation in one sensory stream
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:17.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,will automatically associate experiences on another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,People with such a special ability are very rare,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:23.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and the number of researches in our country are very few.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to research\Nusing fMRI and SPECT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the activity of the brain in each region,\Nand its relevance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:33.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By all means, I'd like to count with Shinya-kun's cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's an unusual case, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes, it'll be a very interesting research.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nice, please, do it by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:44.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I object.\N{\3c&H573235&}What's your objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:47.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why don't you cooperate?\NIt's a nice research.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:50.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun can't bear the examinations with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,of fMRI or SPECT.\N{\3c&H573235&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a doctor, you probably know the\Nhardship that children with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:01.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Autism spectrum have to suffer, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:05.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They can't deal with unexpected situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even in their daily life has steps to follow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,they have to live their life with much predictability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:14.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of those things.\N{\3c&H573235&}Forcing the big sound close to his ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for a long period of time with the same posture,\Ninside of the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is an environment that Shinya can't possible bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,During SPECT test, we could use a sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop making fun of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:30.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you thought, even once, what it feels to be in his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How much they have to struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to live in this society,\Nhave you thought about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't listen to your patients,\Nyou can't possibly know, but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:42.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,every minute using the air around,\Nthey desperately trying to stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You, that don't even try\Nto understand those hardships,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:47.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't leave Shinya-kun to your care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's a haughty attitude, Hino-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:53.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you in a position to judge Miyagawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because,\Nhaven't you been obsessed with one patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\N{\3c&H573235&}I mean Yumeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:03.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're also been selfish.\N{\3c&H573235&}She has her own circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a doctor's duty\Nto match the needs of the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:09.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kiryuu-kun is a part of our staff, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it enough to have the approval of the mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's fine if Hino-kun stops being in charge.\N{\3c&H573235&}If now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:17.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you push to get the permission from the mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you'll break the bond between mother and son,\Nthey've been building till now with much effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For Shinya-kun, his mother is his lifeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:27.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, stop this!\N{\3c&H573235&}Miyagawa-kun, just get her permission immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun, you're not in charge of him anymore, okay?\N{\3c&H573235&}I can't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you out of Yumeno's case too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well then, there's nothing left but to quit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:43.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun, cool off that hot head of yours\Nand then give us an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:45.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:56.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, what follow is\Nthe communication of the parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have my hopes on this.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What was that? Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, but\NI refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why?\NBy all means, please, I ask for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is because of Hino?\N{\3c&H573235&}Is not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:27.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you refuse this,\Nit will be difficult to stay here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you consider this one more time?\N{\3c&H573235&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:34.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because my feelings won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya! Wait! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please put that back, Shinya
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:57.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Again ... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is causing Shinya-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a tough experience, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is my fault for getting\Nemotional at the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I refuse directly to Dr. Miyagawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:16.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., you don't have to worry anymore,\Nplease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:18.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:21:00.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:03.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is open, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:07.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:09.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Am I interrupting you..?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it? Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:33.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About Shinya-kun's incident
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:36.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize to that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:43.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well.. when I met him for the first time here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the one who messed up the\Nminiature garden and the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:49.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it was me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:54.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And Shinya-kun put them in order again,\Nwithout looking unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:04.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wish to convey clearly\Na proper apology..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:07.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san,\Nplease don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That wasn't your doing,\Nbut Yumeno-san who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:12.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..\N{\3c&H573235&}And
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:17.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun loves setting up\Nthings that have fallen down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:20.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He would virtually pass unnoticed\Nto adults around him, but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:24.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that kid has a great personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.56,0:22:33.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:35.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's a cute stuffed toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:37.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..this..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:41.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This, could you give this to Shinya-kun,\Ndoctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:45.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and tell him that I'm sorry for not\Napologizing that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:49.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun will be happy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:51.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:57.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:02.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Instead of worrying about me, are you okay doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:05.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:11.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It seems like you are being forced by something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm wonder if something had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:30.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Actually, now I was thinking\Nof apologizing to Shinya-kun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:35.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though I call myself his friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:38.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything good\Nfor that child,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:42.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:48.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About Shinya-kun, it seems like he\Nwants to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:50.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And that..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:54.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think the Dr. is the only one\Nwho can get to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:58.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:02.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:06.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to thank..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:10.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A psychiatrist not only treats patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:14.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,they can also be saved\Nby the words of a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:16.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Like me, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:23.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.03,0:24:34.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.55,0:24:37.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, about Shinya-kun, I'll leave this to you..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:41.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About that, Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.13,0:24:47.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you could give this directly to\NShinya-kun would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:51.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow we're doing a party\Nto celebrate Shinya-kun's award at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.05,0:24:53.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Friends from the hospital are also coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.54,0:24:55.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you like,\Nwould you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.56,0:24:58.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, me, at that kind of place..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.56,0:25:01.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, you're shy to strangers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.58,0:25:05.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My favorite comedian has this saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.55,0:25:11.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Being shy is a wonderful talent\Nreceived from god"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.54,0:25:14.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:16.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.55,0:25:20.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you said this yourself,\Nthe others will think it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:24.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In that way, if that the first thing\Nyou can led others to think
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.05,0:25:26.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,then that's a great talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.54,0:25:33.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since tomorrow is holidays,\Nso the celebration will be from midday.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.53,0:25:36.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It would be great if you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.64,0:25:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.05,0:25:54.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then.\N{\3c&H573235&}I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:00.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.04,0:26:04.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I said it twice..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.61,0:26:08.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, you liked these, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.08,0:26:10.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it eclair?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.55,0:26:13.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, not so much recently..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.55,0:26:16.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ah, but since you troubled,\NI'll receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.56,0:26:22.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun also comes here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.24,0:26:27.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ah.. that has to do with your duty of confidentiality,\Nso you can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:30.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If the other party is you, then it's \Nto hell with confidentiality, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.06,0:26:36.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's it that you want to hear about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.54,0:26:39.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, today, it's about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.40,0:26:41.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.16,0:26:46.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akari-kun, don't you feel like coming back to our hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.09,0:26:50.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You surely don't want to end up\Nlistening the complaints
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.64,0:26:53.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,of the patients at\Na dumping place like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.54,0:26:56.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well about that..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.68,0:27:00.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to aim the top at the The White Tower\Nonce more?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.53,0:27:15.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.49,0:27:19.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun, let's toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.50,0:27:22.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., did you prepare all of this?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.51,0:27:24.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mash potato curry,\Npseudo tandoori chicken,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.48,0:27:27.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ponzu garland chrysanthemum, and so on.\NLet's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.48,0:27:29.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya, it's the toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.50,0:27:32.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Shinya's celebration, here, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.55,0:27:36.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So to celebrate the Shinya-kun's \NChildren's Art Exhibition Grand Prix ..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.99,0:27:39.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,let's toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.99,0:27:41.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.49,0:27:45.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun seems to really like\Nthat spot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:49.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. the ones who should be thankful\Nare Shinya and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.48,0:27:51.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About today, I'm really\Nthankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.68,0:27:55.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, I just like to stay friends\Nwith Shinya-kun, it's just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.36,0:27:56.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.92,0:28:00.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Someone is still coming?\NAh Madoka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.32,0:28:03.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka is also coming but,\NI invited Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.36,0:28:09.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And then, today, we have another\Nreason to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.00,0:28:11.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-kun, please.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.06,0:28:18.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've decided to accept studying abroad\Nat the Texas Houston Psychiatrist School.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.56,0:28:21.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, Rintaro's study abroad destination?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.08,0:28:25.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll seek to learn the\Nempathetic treatment in the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.60,0:28:27.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and become a full-fledged psychiatrist \Nas Dr. Hino is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.28,0:28:30.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wow ~ Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.12,0:28:32.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good luck.\NDo your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.04,0:28:34.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\3c&H573235&}Kawakami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.56,0:28:37.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,without trying so hard, do your best.\N{\3c&H573235&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.44,0:28:41.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I've been really under your care until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.64,0:28:44.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-san!\NFrom the bottom of my heart I'll be cheering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.51,0:28:49.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, to celebrate Kawakami Yoko's departure,\Nonce more, let's toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.49,0:28:51.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, let's toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.01,0:28:54.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.08,0:28:56.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, Fukuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.00,0:28:58.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.00,0:29:01.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is that?\NI'm completely okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.49,0:29:02.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.99,0:29:05.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's let them drink big time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.80,0:29:06.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.40,0:29:13.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of talk\NShinya-kun is having with Yasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.60,0:29:16.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I could become Yasuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.49,0:29:20.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I could get to understand that kid more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.99,0:29:25.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Texas Houston!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.50,0:29:27.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Houston, Texas-! right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.54,0:29:36.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the other day.\N{\3c&H573235&}Ah..no
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.51,0:29:39.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.49,0:29:42.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you want to leave a message, I could tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.50,0:29:44.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.56,0:29:49.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you have no business with him,\Ncoming to his place on a holiday it's an intrusion 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.84,0:29:51.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.64,0:29:54.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since you're my brother's patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.59,0:29:57.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want to send you away\Ncoldhearted or something like that, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.50,0:30:01.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're not his only patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.02,0:30:04.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.02,0:30:05.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Also, my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.99,0:30:09.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,has a girlfriend,\NYuriko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.01,0:30:14.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's how things are..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.06,0:30:16.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.99,0:30:25.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother,it's not good unless\Nyou properly lock the door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.01,0:30:27.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look Rintaro\NMadoka-chan is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.51,0:30:30.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Madoka, you're late
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.00,0:30:32.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello, sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.09,0:30:41.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.51,0:30:46.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Before being betrayed,\Nit's better if I betray him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.49,0:30:50.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,See you, Hino-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.98,0:31:06.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Kaoru-san\Nis intending to leave the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.98,0:31:09.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to protect Shinya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:14.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By the way, Yumeno-san\Ndidn't come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.99,0:31:16.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.01,0:31:24.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with\Npsychiatrists  falling in love~!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:27.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.99,0:31:32.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I knew this was going to happen,\NI'd have got ridden of the Dr.'s opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.99,0:31:35.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I should have confessed my love for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.48,0:31:38.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.01,0:31:40.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.05,0:31:43.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The person Fukuhara-kun was in love with is Kawakami-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.50,0:31:45.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You two, what are you talking about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.50,0:31:49.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,♪～ {\i1} If only I could express to you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:52.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,♪～ {\i1}“I love you”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.49,0:31:56.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,♪～ {\i1}Even if you don't answer\NEven if you look bothered...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:18.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.50,0:32:22.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Help me,\NI'm being chased by debt collectors again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.49,0:32:26.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with your mom being killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.56,0:32:27.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What if you're killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.01,0:32:32.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since that damn doctor appeared\Nyou've changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.96,0:32:34.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Before, you were kinder, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.84,0:32:36.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't you help mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.92,0:32:39.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you in love with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:41.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.68,0:32:45.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.\N{\3c&H573235&}Then what..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.56,0:32:48.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's deceiving Akira\Ninto trying to erase me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.52,0:32:50.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't allow that, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.49,0:32:54.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please I need 10 million yen\Nsomehow really soon..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.51,0:32:59.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or I'll be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.01,0:33:02.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.01,0:33:04.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,how about using this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.01,0:33:17.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.00,0:33:22.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,, It's a interesting picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.50,0:33:26.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.51,0:33:32.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kiryuu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.00,0:33:38.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Won't you think about it one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.52,0:33:43.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., my opinion won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.56,0:33:47.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since there is a meeting,\Nexcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.56,0:34:04.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh? What happened? Shinya-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.50,0:34:07.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today\Nit's not the day we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.52,0:34:16.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.03,0:34:21.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The hiragana?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.00,0:34:26.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,o\N{\3c&H573235&}o?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.52,0:34:30.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute,\NI'll write on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.32,0:34:33.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
