Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.52,0:40:07.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.10,0:40:14.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.52,0:40:18.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you are a tough kid, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.80,0:40:35.28,Remembering,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(532.8,396.2)}I've got to live longer than the doctors.\NAnd if I become a dad I don't want our children to be troubled like me.\NAs mom is doing her best for me, I also want to do my best\NSo, I'll go into the machine, in that way,\Nthe important doctors may come up with a new treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.03,0:40:32.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.58,0:40:37.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun has been properly thinking about this,\Nmore than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.51,0:40:49.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.02,0:40:54.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, right? Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.07,0:40:58.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since it's what Shinya-kun wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.03,0:41:19.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.50,0:41:21.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey Shinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.52,0:41:26.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you don't have to try it too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.02,0:41:33.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it's unpleasant,\Nit's okay to ask to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.01,0:41:48.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.64,0:41:50.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll leave him under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.01,0:41:52.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.36,0:41:57.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.52,0:42:01.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.59,0:42:06.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About the bicycles,\NI think they fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.01,0:42:08.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.08,0:42:11.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, when the kid scratched the car
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.50,0:42:14.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think Shinya-kun was just picking up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.50,0:42:18.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the bikes which have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.52,0:42:22.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He dislikes when the bikes are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.06,0:42:25.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, even though he didn't \Nknock them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.51,0:42:28.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he was picking them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.00,0:42:32.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If adults see this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.50,0:42:36.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,they would get angry at him,\Nthinking it's his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.40,0:42:41.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But it's wrong, Prof. Miyagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.16,0:42:44.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The ones who should be scolded, instead of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.11,0:42:47.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's us,\Nfor not trying to understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.02,0:42:50.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's always tried really hard
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.02,0:42:53.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,doing his best effort in order\Nto understand us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.76,0:42:59.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The most painful thing for the person suffering from
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.50,0:43:03.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Autism spectrum\Nand their surrounding family
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.07,0:43:07.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is not being possible to communicate\Nby means of oral language.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.76,0:43:10.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The miracle that has happened now with Shinya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.01,0:43:14.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is a hope for many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.01,0:43:15.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.01,0:43:19.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I ask your favor, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.00,0:43:21.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In any way, using your knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.52,0:43:24.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please, decipher his signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.88,0:43:29.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.01,0:43:35.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, we're starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.02,0:43:38.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You'll hear a loud sound,\Nbut don't be afraid, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.02,0:43:44.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This, it seems to be you, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.59,0:43:51.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And then,\Nthis must be Shinya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.00,0:43:54.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Before the examination, using these,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.02,0:43:58.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he tried to explain\Nwhy he wanted to go through the examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.01,0:44:13.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.00,0:44:16.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.01,0:44:20.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}want..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.51,0:44:22.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.05,0:44:26.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}protect..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.00,0:44:29.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.03,0:44:37.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.51,0:44:41.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Parents who have children with Autism spectrum
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.08,0:44:44.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,unconsciously tend to blame themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.50,0:44:48.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something happened during breast-feeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.02,0:44:52.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I do something to this child
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.01,0:44:54.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that shouldn't be done, during pregnancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.51,0:44:59.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But the mother did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.53,0:45:03.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun knows that,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.10,0:45:06.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,knows that his mom, for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.52,0:45:09.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she will do anything, no matter how hard
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.53,0:45:12.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,no matter how much effort it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.53,0:45:16.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun knows that perfectly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.52,0:45:25.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why he wants to protect his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.01,0:45:39.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.52,0:45:42.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.59,0:45:50.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.50,0:45:52.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.52,0:45:55.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please do not quit the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.51,0:45:59.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun has been growing  up firmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.51,0:46:04.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From now on, together,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.01,0:46:07.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,let's us also have some growth. 
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.52,0:46:16.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.01,0:46:26.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.50,0:46:28.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.51,0:46:51.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though I respect Dr. Hino\Nfrom the bottom of my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.01,0:46:54.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there's only one thing I don't agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.00,0:46:55.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.50,0:47:00.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't think love is like a\Ntemporal mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.54,0:47:04.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then..\N{\3c&H573235&}It's a genuine mental disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.53,0:47:12.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I think it was good\Nto be rejected by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.02,0:47:21.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.04,0:47:25.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-san, you do your best too.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.08,0:47:26.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.50,0:47:34.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.53,0:47:44.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.53,0:47:47.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,.. so you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.55,0:47:50.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Fukuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.11,0:48:07.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.03,0:48:13.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.00,0:48:22.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.53,0:48:32.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hasumi, have you forgotten my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.03,0:48:35.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Araki.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.64,0:48:40.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So you haven't forgotten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.52,0:48:56.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.54,0:48:59.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, how was the image diagnosis of the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.52,0:49:02.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When the issue of the language is challenged,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.04,0:49:05.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the normal blood flow\Nnot only increases in the left temporal lobe
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.61,0:49:08.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but also in the parietal lobe,\Nwhich performs spatial recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.02,0:49:11.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is more, the main\Nblood flow in the right side is increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.02,0:49:15.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Such data, with a clear image of Synesthesia in\Nchildren is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.02,0:49:17.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,even worldwide, very rare, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.51,0:49:20.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing! You did it.\N{\3c&H573235&}Hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.53,0:49:23.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What ? Is it okay to let Miyagawa get all the credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.58,0:49:27.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm satisfied just with the fact\Nthat I was able to convey Shinya-kun's thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.04,0:49:30.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to his mother.\N{\3c&H573235&}You need to want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.51,0:49:34.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And, that woman's treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.03,0:49:35.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is it going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.01,0:49:41.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, is she an appointment patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.05,0:49:43.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She is Akira-san's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.59,0:49:46.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. this person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.02,0:49:49.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're also a doctor?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.52,0:49:54.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What happens when psychiatrists put a hand\Non their patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.03,0:49:56.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well,\Nif you actually put a hand on the patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.51,0:49:58.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that basically\Nis a violation of Medical Ethics,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.53,0:50:00.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but this guy,\Nis not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.54,0:50:02.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How do you know that is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.59,0:50:06.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, because this guy is a virtuous gentleman\Nwearing a white robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.51,0:50:08.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.53,0:50:12.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.04,0:50:19.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.54,0:50:23.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So the 'rin' in Hino Rintaro is just\Nthe 'rin' in ethics violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.54,0:50:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,34.6)}She's making a play of sounds, ethics violation=[rinri ihan]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.63,0:50:29.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be sued for this photo,\Nwanna buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.53,0:50:31.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I refuse, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.53,0:50:33.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Calm down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.52,0:50:36.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then for this picture, how much\Nare you asking for selling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.04,0:50:39.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The doctor over here gets what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.01,0:50:43.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How about 50 million? [~420,353 USD]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.53,0:50:45.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You said 50 million..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.10,0:50:49.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You wanna pay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.50,0:50:52.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Rintaro, the medical ethics transgressor.
